  "items": [
    {
      "id": "25998467",
      "text": "भारत ने किया बैलिस्टिक मिसाइल का सफल परीक्षण, पाक-चीन को मिलेगा करारा जवाब",
      "audio": "hi/unknown/hi_u_25998467.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "25998467",
        "gender": "u",
        "up_votes": 2,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 6.16
    },
    {
      "id": "26010468",
      "text": "साउथ दिल्ली नगर निगम सख्त, शॉपिंग मॉल के बाहर नहीं दिखेंगे होर्डिंग",
      "audio": "hi/unknown/hi_u_26010468.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "26010468",
        "gender": "u",
        "up_votes": 2,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 7.52
    },
    {
      "id": "27371674",
      "text": "बनारस के मुस्लिम बहुल इलाकों में भारी मतदान",
      "audio": "hi/unknown/hi_u_27371674.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "27371674",
        "gender": "u",
        "up_votes": 2,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
      "id": "26350865",
      "text": "चेन्नई में बदमाशों ने चलती ट्रेन में लहराए हथियार, वीडियो वायरल",
      "audio": "hi/unknown/hi_u_26350865.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "26350865",
        "gender": "u",
        "up_votes": 2,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 4.1
    },
    {
      "id": "27500578",
      "text": "डेट के लिए तैयार हैं शेरॉन",
      "audio": "hi/unknown/hi_u_27500578.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "27500578",
        "gender": "u",
        "up_votes": 2,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 3.42
    },
    {
      "id": "26120088",
      "text": "सुपरमॉडल इरीना शायक की 'गुड मॉर्निंग' सेल्फी",
      "audio": "hi/unknown/hi_u_26120088.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "26120088",
        "gender": "u",
        "up_votes": 2,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
      "id": "27509026",
      "text": "केरल हाई कोर्ट में कई पदों के लिए नौकरी",
      "audio": "hi/unknown/hi_u_27509026.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "27509026",
        "gender": "u",
        "up_votes": 2,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 3.42
    },
    {
      "id": "26043843",
      "text": "कैमरे के सामने मुस्कुराने से घबराते थे अनिल, ये थी वजह",
      "audio": "hi/unknown/hi_u_26043843.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "26043843",
        "gender": "u",
        "up_votes": 2,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 4.03
    },
    {
      "id": "26236234",
      "text": "नक्सलवाद की जड़ों तक पहुंचना जरूरी: सोनिया",
      "audio": "hi/unknown/hi_u_26236234.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "26236234",
        "gender": "u",
        "up_votes": 3,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 3.53
    },
    {
      "id": "26358151",
      "text": "प्रेमी की बेवफाई से आहत प्रेमिका ने उठाया खौफनाक कदम",
      "audio": "hi/unknown/hi_u_26358151.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "26358151",
        "gender": "u",
        "up_votes": 2,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 5.44
    },
    {
      "id": "26060498",
      "text": "उसने मुझे मुँह पर मुक्का मारा।",
      "audio": "hi/unknown/hi_u_26060498.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "26060498",
        "gender": "u",
        "up_votes": 2,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 3.64
    },
    {
      "id": "26033338",
      "text": "उसने मुझपर ग़लती करने का इलज़ाम लगाया।",
      "audio": "hi/unknown/hi_u_26033338.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "26033338",
